				<outline text="New OPML Editor feature: &lt;a href=&quot;http://support.opml.org/2006/08/27#a1631&quot;&gt;Portable rivers&lt;/a&gt;." created="Tue, 29 Aug 2006 06:37:46 GMT"/>
