				<outline text="Ed Cone has an interesting &lt;a href=&quot;http://blog.eweek.com/blogs/knowitall/archive/2006/08/23/12672.aspx&quot;&gt;perspective&lt;/a&gt; on NYTimesRiver. " created="Wed, 23 Aug 2006 20:39:40 GMT"/>
				<outline text="The German version of Wikipedia is &lt;a href=&quot;http://arstechnica.com/news.ars/post/20060823-7569.html&quot;&gt;getting gatekeepers&lt;/a&gt;, on an experimental basis. Experienced users will approve changes before they go live. This could cut down on vandalism, but what else will it cut down on?" created="Wed, 23 Aug 2006 23:16:44 GMT"/>
				<outline text="Just curious, &lt;a href=&quot;http://mymoblog.wordpress.com/2006/08/23/what-tools/&quot;&gt;what tools do people use&lt;/a&gt; to post to their blogs from a Blackberry or Treo? " created="Wed, 23 Aug 2006 17:50:14 GMT"/>
				<outline text="I'm hosting a mobile version of the &lt;a href=&quot;http://buzzmachine.scripting.com/&quot;&gt;BuzzMachine&lt;/a&gt; blog." created="Wed, 23 Aug 2006 15:11:42 GMT"/>
