				<outline text="There's a pretty funny podcast coming out tomorrow over on Pajama Media; an interview by Andrew Keen, of yours truly." created="Fri, 18 Aug 2006 03:11:08 GMT"/>
				<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.davosnewbies.com/2006/08/17/only-in-berkeley/&quot;&gt;Lance Knobel&lt;/a&gt;: &quot;On Heinz Avenue in slightly industrial west Berkeley, there was a large farm truck, with its ramp down. Gleefully charging out of the truck was a large drove of goats, being herded into a derelict, hugely overgrown site.&quot;" created="Fri, 18 Aug 2006 05:04:55 GMT"/>
