				<outline text="I've spent a lot of time hanging out with &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.calacanis.com/2006/08/06/no-im-not-starting-a-wikipedia-competitor-killer-or-viable-c/&quot;&gt;Jason Calacanis&lt;/a&gt; at this &lt;a href=&quot;http://wikimania2006.wikimedia.org/wiki/Schedule&quot;&gt;conference&lt;/a&gt;. Smart guy. Lots of ideas flying around, in all directions. " created="Sun, 06 Aug 2006 16:19:19 GMT"/>
